{"tid":1351934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[辦公室文宣入] 係時候教化下仲有少少理性嘅中間派","createTime":"2019-07-22T16:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:56:15.000Z","uid":115037,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d1a58f5b5580523f91461900057c2c7b66b84560","tid":1351934,"uid":115037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"近呢幾日發生嘅事  發現其實可以試下教化一班會稍為諗下野 理性嘅 淺藍屍<br />\n<br />\n多一個自己人都好吖<br />\n呢班通常係有受過下教育嘅老屎忽<br />\n<br />\n認為可以試下copy 全公司email address<br />\n有內地或海外同事更佳<br />\n<br />\n再用新gmail account send 以下PDF 俾公司所有同事，記得bcc <br />\n希望有人睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整左中英文version ，寫得唔好 我再改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZbdGDG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZbdGDG.png&h=c1590ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SbY7L5o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSbY7L5o.png&h=548ed333&s={SIZE}\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n唔知呢個方法係咪可以保密到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇得upload PDF  惟有up 相"},{"pid":"b814fbd911ee92cc9e10d702819d03f6a54bdbd7","tid":1351934,"uid":115037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:54:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f27ab912fe8308779f16c53012c6f0ab8417024","tid":1351934,"uid":115037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:55:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4173ec826f8706533516b23504e89dc348d8b652","tid":1351934,"uid":115037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:55:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d7f9621febd38717b24cf4556703bdc72622418b","tid":1351934,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:57:51.000Z","msg":"［緊急］724 725 726 全面塞鐵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請大家入黎投個票，表達下意見"},{"pid":"44b2ca520bd070168d79b1a9e52a15337807300d","tid":1351934,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:58:10.000Z","msg":"［緊急］724 725 726 全面塞鐵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請大家入黎投個票，表達下意見"},{"pid":"fcbf19548e65aca04bb4799a6ce90173016ebaab","tid":1351934,"uid":115037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"86cf99b9d8abef047d087990a0239f5f1535f02b","tid":1351934,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:58:48.000Z","msg":"From Simon Lui (Facebook)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156060495911105&amp;set=a.45435071104&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10156060495911105%26set%3Da.45435071104%26type%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn29TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=67b6c062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156060495911105&amp;set=a.45435071104&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n我經歷過波士頓馬拉松爆炸案，明白襲擊後的恐怖<br />\n1) 爆炸前30分鐘，我仍在Boylston st現場，只是早走了<br />\n2) MIT校警就在我Lab樓下(Building 32)被槍殺，只是我偷懶無返工(偷懶萬歲)<br />\n<br />\n我嗰晚好驚，本來諗住「一星期唔出街，以後見人都要提防」... 但原來我錯了<br />\n<br />\n【恐佈分子的目的，不是要讓100人死掉，而是要令幾億人害怕】<br />\n<br />\n是波士頓人教曉我，面對恐懼就要更勇敢。因為爆炸後第二晚，波士頓人竟然這樣：<br />\n- 不躲在家中，照常出街跑步<br />\n- 不讓恐懼擴散，反而故意外出食飯購物<br />\n- 人與人之間的信任沒有動搖。反而整網頁讓居民登記，開放自己家，讓因爆炸案錯過火車的旅人住一晚 <br />\n<br />\n「開放自己家！黐線㗎！引狼入室！」不是的<br />\n- 若恐佈分子要襲擊，點會無方法？<br />\n- 由華盛頓來旅行但錯過火車嘅自己人，點會睇唔出？幫佢點會有事？<br />\n- 自己人互相幫助，其實安全得很<br />\n- 所以最後，我自己都踩單車出去飲咖啡，重買水比站崗嘅人<br />\n<br />\n恐佈分子的失敗，在於居民鎮定不害怕，在於鄰里關係沒有動搖。若要防範恐佈分子，不是要人人自危，而是要把問題源頭清掉吧。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，守望相助，不要落單，齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e2f7f757560fd974084247d736947ef2b4a462","tid":1351934,"uid":115037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:18:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"52f0635cbcaafd2e0c3ce3ae749a87637a173445","tid":1351934,"uid":115037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:22:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cee1b444f2d69f8f87fdfc4bbd0e0d58e4efad50","tid":1351934,"uid":115037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:39:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"373c74b3ed92fded0637bdd949c2db6b96cf3b19","tid":1351934,"uid":115037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:03:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1ff089169dbd0261ac12b4712f0f229e643b186a","tid":1351934,"uid":115037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:00:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"43226c859cca1e888f0ca4fc25e1ad2e697053ef","tid":1351934,"uid":115037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:56:15.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}